{
  "name": "Heraldic Banner",
  "type": "feature",
  "img": "icons/sundries/flags/banner-standard-blue.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": "<p>You have a <strong>Heraldic Banner </strong>that&rsquo;s made from a 10ft (3m) pole&nbsp;with an attached 2ft x 4ft (60cm x 120cm) flag.</p>\n<p>The banner bears the emblem of your group, guild, faction, kingdom, or other affiliated group.</p>\n<p>A creature can spend <strong>1 AP</strong> to plant or pick up the banner on the ground within 1 Space.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Display Banner</strong></span></p>\n<p>You must display a <strong>Banner </strong>for a creature to benefit from its&nbsp;presence. You can display the banner by carrying it with at&nbsp;least 1 free hand or by planting it on the ground.</p>\n<p>The banner is not considered on display while it&rsquo;s lying on the ground, in the possession of an enemy creature, or its emblem is defaced or torn.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Banner Actions</strong></span></p>\n<p>While your banner is on display, you can take 1 of the follow Banner Actions:</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.dc20rpg.classes.Item.OCXDjuG7khpwg42E]{Bolster Allies}</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.dc20rpg.classes.Item.Q2kfvagJSfH8vBTp]{Rally Allies}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Replacing the Banner</strong><br></span></p>\n<p>If you ever lose your&nbsp;<strong>Heraldic Banner</strong>, you can have a new&nbsp;crafted for 5g in most towns.</p>\n<p>Alternatively, you can spend 2g for the materials and make it yourself.</p>\n<p>You can attempt to craft a new Banner once during each <strong>Long Rest </strong>by using <strong>Weaver&rsquo;s Tools </strong>and succeeding a DC 15 <strong>Weaving Check</strong>.</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">&nbsp;</span></p>",
